    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small spoons, made of silver, bone, ivory, or wood, used to bring snuff from a container to the nose, or from a larger container to a smaller.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
